name: xontrib-readable-traceback
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "xontrib-readable-traceback" %}
{% set version = "0.3.2" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: d43feeca2037035767f483da9238a085c9194f9232d9638cae80642cca7f1593

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - colorama
    - python-backtrace
    - xonsh

test:
  commands:
    - test -f "${SP_DIR}/xontrib/readable-traceback.xsh"

about:
  home: https://github.com/6syun9/xontrib-readable-traceback
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Make traceback easier to see for xonsh'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - scopatz
